Author: Alexis Krier
PONG with HTML5 and some Jquery.

INSTALL:
Take all the file in a directory, open pong.html with a good browser ;)

Player1:
A Q for moving
S to give a direction front forward to the ball.

Player2:
arrow up down for moving
arrow left to give a direction front forward to the ball.

Both player:
Moving in the opposite direction of the ball during the collision make it to bounce in the opposite way :)

Have fun